room_title: Escape room "Bustin’ Out of the Eighties" by Whole Brain Escape in Raleigh - Durham
review: Did the 80's Room with some friends, it was a ton of fun! The clues were clever and difficult. Nothing was unreasonably difficult or too easy, and the music was great! Definitely going back for the other room!

room_title: Escape room "Bustin’ Out of the Eighties" by Whole Brain Escape in Raleigh - Durham
review: We visited Whole Brain for our 30th room escape. We loved it! Highly recommend the 80s room. Well thought out. Decent level of difficulty without getting frustrated.

room_title: Escape room "Bustin’ Out of the Eighties" by Whole Brain Escape in Raleigh - Durham
review: My husband, four of our friends, and I had the amazing opportunity to visit Whole Brain Escape and escape from the 80s. We all had a wonderful time! I love puzzles and games and am very competitive so this was a great way to spend the afternoon.  Some of the puzzles are tricky, but as first timers it was still easy enough to figure out.  I can't wait to go back and do the Supervillain room.
